languages.text: "Я бы принял ваше предложение, но у нас еще есть медкомплекты. Немного, но на путь к шаттлам хватит — а большего и не надо".
"I would have accepted your offer, but we still have medicae kits. Not many, but it should last us until we get to the shuttles — which is all we need."

languages.text: "Ich würde Euer Angebot annehmen, aber noch haben wir einige Medicae-Kits. Nicht viele, aber sie sollten reichen, um zu den Shuttles zu kommen ... das ist alles, was wir brauchen."

languages.text: « J'aurais accepté votre proposition en d'autres circonstances, mais il nous reste encore des kits de medicae. Pas beaucoup, mais ils devraient nous permettre de tenir jusqu'aux navettes. Nous n'avons pas besoin de plus. »

languages.text: «Habría aceptado su oferta, pero aún nos quedan botiquines. No muchos, pero deberían bastar hasta que lleguemos a las lanzaderas, y es cuanto necesitamos».

languages.text: “我也很愿意接受你的提议，但我们手上还有医疗包。虽然不太多，但足够我们支撑到穿梭机那里，这足够了。”
languages.original_text: "I would have accepted your offer, but we still have medicae kits. Not many, but it should last us until we get to the shuttles — which is all we need."

traits.locale_text: “我也很愿意接受你的提议，但我们手上还有医疗包。虽然不太多，但足够我们支撑到穿梭机那里，这足够了。”

languages.text: 「申し出はありがたいですが、まだメディキットが残っています。数は多くありませんが、シャトルに辿り着くまではもつはずです。それだけあれば十分です」
languages.original_text: "I would have accepted your offer, but we still have medicae kits. Not many, but it should last us until we get to the shuttles — which is all we need."

languages.text: "Teklifinizi kabul etmek isterdim ama sıhhiye çantalarımız var. Gerçi çok da kalmadı, mekiklere varana dek işimizi görsünler yeter."
